{"tha-ap288:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap288:0.2":"Pannadayakavagga ","tha-ap288:0.3":"6 Upatthakadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap288:1.1":"“Rathiyam patipajjantam, ","tha-ap288:1.2":"ahutinam patiggaham; ","tha-ap288:1.3":"Dvipadindam mahanagam, ","tha-ap288:1.4":"lokajettham narasabham. ","tha-ap288:2.1":"Pakkosapiya tassaham, ","tha-ap288:2.2":"sabbalokahitesino; ","tha-ap288:2.3":"Upatthako maya dinno, ","tha-ap288:2.4":"siddhatthassa mahesino. ","tha-ap288:3.1":"Patiggahetva sambuddho, ","tha-ap288:3.2":"niyyadesi mahamuni; ","tha-ap288:3.3":"Utthaya asana tamha, ","tha-ap288:3.4":"pakkami pacinamukho. ","tha-ap288:4.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap288:4.2":"upatthakamadam tada; ","tha-ap288:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap288:4.4":"upatthanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap288:5.1":"Sattapannasito kappe, ","tha-ap288:5.2":"balasenasanamako; ","tha-ap288:5.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap288:5.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap288:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap288:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap288:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap288:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma upatthakadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap288:8.1":"Upatthakadayakattherassapadanam chattham. "}